{"lemma":"شَفَراتِ","slug":"شَفَراتِ","root":"ش.ف.ر","root_slug":"ش-ف-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ف-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22623","n22624","n22625"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"large knife"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"blade (of a sword or knife)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"razor blade"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"brink, edge, verge"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cipher, code"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From شَفْر (šafr), the edge of the eyelid from which the eyelashes grow.\n\nFrom شِفْر (šifr, “cipher”), from French chiffre, from Arabic صِفْر (ṣifr, “zero”), from صَفِرَ (ṣafira, “to be empty”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22623","headword_ar":"شَفْرَةٌ","root":"$fr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large knife;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iforapN","text_ar":"شِفْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", though this is mentioned only by the author of the Mgh; (MF; [but it is not in my copy of the Mgh; and Golius mentions ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uforapN","text_ar":"شُفْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as having this signification, on the authority of Meyd;]) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a broad knife:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ifaArN","text_ar":"شِفَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afaraAtN","text_ar":"شَفَرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and [coll. gen. n., of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iforapN","text_ar":"شِفْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un., or it may be a quasi-pl. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aforapN","text_ar":"شَفْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iforN","text_ar":"شِفْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (Mgh, TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A servant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, TA;) because of his utility. (TA.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSogaru Alqawomi","text_ar":"اَصْغَرُ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aforatuhumo","text_ar":"شَفْرَتُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The least of the party is their servant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A shoemaker's knife."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of iron made broad, and edged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pointed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A broad blade:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says the author of the Mgh. (TA. [But not in my copy of the Mgh.]) ―         -b6-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cutting part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Had~","text_ar":"حَدّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) of a sword: (S, Mgh, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge of the cutting part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a sword. (TA. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ubaAbN","text_ar":"ذُبَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a blade: (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each of the two sides"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof. (AHn, TA.) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Each of the two sharp sides"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edges of a spear-head and of an arrow-head."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b7-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uforN","text_ar":"شُفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", second sentence."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","K","TA","S"]},{"entry_id":"n22624","headword_ar":"شُفْرَةٌ","root":"$fr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n22625","headword_ar":"شِفْرَةٌ","root":"$fr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}